2002-02-11 16:59  Guus Sliepen <guus@sliepen.warande.net>

	* THANKS, configure.in, doc/tinc.conf.5, doc/tinc.texi, m4/zlib.m4,
	po/nl.po, src/net.c, src/node.c, src/node.h, src/protocol.h,
	src/protocol_key.c: Added support for packet compression, thanks to
	Mark Glines.  Add "Compression = <level>" to the host config files,
	where level can be 0 (off), or any integer between 1 (fast) and 9
	(best).  

