	* src/: connection.c, connection.h, net.c, protocol.c, route.c: 
	Added purge_tree for connection_t's which are no longer in the
	connection, active or id trees, but which may still be referenced.
	This tree is flushed when it is safe, this replaces
	purge_connection_tree().  
	
	Also lots of bugfixes related to the new trees.  

