	* src/: Makefile.am, connection.c, connection.h, net.c, net.h,
	protocol.c, route.c, route.h: 
	- route.c is now used to determine destination 
	- flags are removed, since they were not used at all. Use options
	instead.  
	- indirectdata works now, tcponly almost...  
	- made functions that don't return useful information void 

