2001-01-13 17:36  Guus Sliepen <guus@sliepen.warande.net>

	* src/: conf.c, conf.h, net.c, tincd.c: 
	- Allow ASN1 style keys to be in the config files.  
	  Note: tinc ignores private key in the main config file, tinc.conf, 
	  because it should really be in a separate file.  
	- When generating new keys, check if name is known and by default
	  append the public key to the host configuration file (otherwise
	rsa_key.pub).  

