	- Added some extra search functions to rbl routines 
	- Fix subnet_lookup() 
	- Reorder some syslog messages to make more sense 
	- daemon() is back 
	- Don't let scripts execute in parallel (gives race conditions, and 
	  anyway something MIGHT just be configured which is necessary for
	  further execution of tinc itself) 
	- Accidently merged check_child() with execute_script().  
	- Small fixes 

2000-11-24 15:13  Ivo Timmermans <itimmermans@bigfoot.com>

	* doc/tinc.texi: Explain how to tell configure where OpenSSL lives.  

2000-11-24 15:13  Ivo Timmermans <itimmermans@bigfoot.com>

	* lib/pidfile.c: Set errno to 0 before trying to kill the other
	process.  

