	- Fixed indirectdata=no problem 
	- Added support for multiple ConnectTo lines in tinc.conf.  

2000-06-27 14:58  Guus Sliepen <guus@sliepen.warande.net>

	* src/protocol.c: 
	- Fixed KEY_CHANGED notification. A lot of notify_others() calls
	  were wrong (first two arguments swapped). Should probably be
	doublechecked.  
	- Don't retry to connect to hosts with different protocol versions.  

