2000-05-30 23:36  Ivo Timmermans <itimmermans@bigfoot.com>

	* src/protocol.c: Only accept an ADD_HOST request for a host that
	already exists in our conn_list if the nexthop field matches the
	sender.  This is a workaround for older clients.  

