2000-05-08 20:44  Guus Sliepen <guus@sliepen.warande.net>

	* src/: conf.c, conf.h, net.c: Added new config variable
	"ProxyMode". If enabled, all outgoing packets are sent to the uplink
	(ConnectTo), which will have to forward them for us (kernel should
	do that). This is for people behind firewalls.  

