	* src/: encr.c, net.c, net.h, netutl.c, protocol.c, protocol.h: 
	Meta protocol overhaul. Tinc is now incompatible with previous
	versions, furthermore this version does NOT work yet because of a
	problem with sending keys (these should be converted to base36 or
	something like that).  It is possible to telnet to the tinc daemon
	now and type some commands by hand though :).  

