2000-04-25 22:50  Guus Sliepen <guus@sliepen.warande.net>

	* src/net.c: When trying to talk to a host that is in the netmask
	of a tinc server but not the tinc server itself, and no keys have
	been exchanged yet, the key request would be directed to the host
	instead of the server. Fixed.  

